data.description: Welcome to this stunning, meticulously maintained two-story home with impeccable curb appeal. The home features solar screens to beat the Texas heat. Downstairs features an oversized garage, master suite, two bedrooms, huge kitchen, dining room, and an office that can easily be converted into a second living room. The upstairs offers a newly built master suite, which could also be utilized as another bedroom or game room. The backyard offers a peaceful oasis with an extended covered patio perfect for outdoor entertaining. The backyard is complete with a 2-tier retaining wall perfect for a future pool. This home offers a dual-zoned AC unit which easily controls the temperature on each level of the home. This community offers amenities such as a pool, playground, high-speed internet, and walking distance to an elementary school. Conveniently located near dining, shopping, and surrounding cities in DFW. It’s time to pack those boxes, you don't want to miss out on this incredible home.
